>However, the opposition in the Ukraine is mixed between “nationalists,” and citizens who are fed up with the corrupt, oppressive government under President Viktor Yanukovych. The Ukrainian parliament just passed a resolution for the security services to restrain their crackdown.

Here he suggests that it was actually Ukraine who was behind the DNC leaks all along:

